    "(2) LVBench [85]: A benchmark on hour-long video understanding across six dimensions, comprising 2094 multiple-choice QA samples.",
    "(3) MLVU [116]: Designed for minute-level video understanding, with 2174 QA samples spanning diverse domains.",
    "We evaluate the average performance of multiple-choice tasks (M-Avg), where videos have an average duration of 653 seconds.",
    "(4) LongVideoBench [90]: Targets long-form referring reasoning that requires retrieval-based QA, with videos averaging 473 seconds.",
    "(5) MVBench [49]: A shortterm video QA benchmark emphasizing temporal reasoning, containing 4K QA pairs over 20 task categories."
